text: Similonedine brunniofasciata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae, and the only species in the genus Similonedine. It was described by Hua in 1993Biolib.cz - Similonedine brunniofasciata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. and is endemic to China (Fujian and Hunan). ==References== Category:Desmiphorini Category:Beetles described in 1992 Category:Endemic fauna of China Category:Monotypic beetle genera
